at cell division,

00:47:46.530 --> 00:47:51.060
and secondly, by signals from other cells.

00:47:51.060 --> 00:47:53.430
The morphogen gradient interpretation

00:47:54.450 --> 00:47:57.170
is an important mechanism for activating

00:47:57.170 --> 00:47:59.820
gene expression in the correct position.

00:47:59.820 --> 00:48:03.440
And lastly, the community effect converts

00:48:03.440 --> 00:48:07.140
gene expression into final cell types.

